**Hunger Games**
==================
**>Update in Progress<**
------------------
	Hunger games is a new mod that we are developing and will hopefully be successful in the future, you dont have any weapons at the start, its a free for all game, where you have to find boxes to get weapons to kill your enemies.


**News in the Beta version**
==================

New 3D skybox is addded we removed the walls and added water instead.

Weapons are randomly spawned in the boxes.

New water texture.

More Boxes.

Fixed sharp edges on some mountains.

24 players.

The round restarts automaticly when theres only 1 left (but only if players dont join in the middle of the game)





**Planned Future**
====================

Arena is planned.

Optimizing.

Servers:
========

	87.98.152.38:27016

> [Hunger Games Beta TRAILER](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-JBKjFgS4cg&feature=youtu.be "Hunger Games Beta TRAILER")

**Hunger Games**
==================

Hunger games is a new mod that we are developing and will hopefully be successful in the future, this is how it looks so far, we have many plans to come up with, this is only a alpha version so please report bugs or any kind of problems you find

**Planned Future**
====================

Hopefully we will make random spawned weapons in the boxes.

Maybe 24 slots, but that depends on if it gets successful.

Arena is planned too.

Hovering trees will be fixed.

Making the map larger.

**Known bugs**
================

Radar is still on.

Ct, and T spawns, we only need one team.

The last one has to kill him self before the round restarts.

This specific puzzle game-type, Haunted Survival, was created by TPSKJarhead and credit is given. This is a newly created game-type so more ad more HS maps will soon be created. Look forward for to some new scary puzzle maps.

This is a super-fun puzzle map where you go from room to room solving little puzzles and escaping death at every turn. After going through rooms upon rooms of puzzles, you can either go two different pathways. So the fun never ends. The map is pitch dark, except for the few lights that slightly keeps up visibility, to add suspense and keep it haunted. Enjoy.

OK so this is the next map in my new HS_ series. Im really trying to get this map type off the ground and make it noticible like surf and zm. This map is a run down garden/graveyard. There is a pool spawn (shown in screenshots) and fog along a pathway. There is a way to get out of spawn,but its secret but you should figure it out quick enough. There are buyzones for both teams once again secrets  :)

This map features:
-Lighting
-Fog along path and above certain water pools
-Lasers in trap room (in screen shots)
-Hover pushers (hint hint corners of BIG bronwn traproom box at mid)
-invisible ladders
-VERY reflective water
-Good close range action ( I hope )

Well I hope you have fun on this map and if you like my HS_ maps let me know so i can make more of these and have my own genre of maps under the map style selection area.
 
-*-THANK YOU AGAIN SHEEPRIDER-*-

THANX

-JARHEAD

**I've modified De_Dust2 to test my new gamemode, it was so good ... then i decided to continue...**

Bored of low player speed, and prefer a Quake-Like gameplay ?

this gamemode is for you ! 

**FAQ :**

-----------------------------------------
**Q**: What does this gamemode ?

**A**: in my new gamemode, the player start with 200hp, his speed and jump are increased by 50%, and you can wear 2 he/smokegrenade at a time like the Flashbang.

-----------------------------------------

**Q**: Why "**HS_**dust2" ?

**A**: HS because my map is really "hardcore", then i decided to call it HARDCORE-STRIKE_DUST2

-----------------------------------------

**Q**: Can i make a map with your gamemode ?

**A**: Not Yet, but i'll add a prefab Later, you can also decompile it. (use my textures too if u make one)

-----------------------------------------

have other questions, or ideas to improve ? ? tell me ^^

HAVE FUN !

---------------------------------------

/!\ **TOO BRIGHTER FOR YOU ?? Use This Version** [hs-dust2-darker](https://dl.dropbox.com/u/88523875/hs_dust2_darker.bsp "") /!\

--------------------------------

**PLEASE READ BEFORE RATING !! Thx**

This is my second map!! There is a lot of advanced lighting in place in the halls and spawns. THERE IS LOTS OF FLASHING just to warn you. Its theme is a run down insane assylum. There are multiple weapon pickup points. Some secret teleporters are also in place!!! Well you should get a good fps and have lots of fun. WARNING: The map is very dark I AM AWARE OF THIS it is suppose to be like this to stay as an on-the-edge-of-your-seat map! Well have fun and there is NO buyzone. I might add a secret one in a later sersions if people want it. Well leave comments NOT FLAME !!! if you dont like it dont d.l it plz :) THANX

-*-SPECIAL THANX GOES OUT TO SHEEPRIDER FOR ALL HIS HELP-*-

-JARHEAD

p.s. the .NAV file is included in the RAR d.l

P.S.S the map is much brighter then the screenshots show :)

hoejhus_remix by Lickwim

This remix of hoejhus features some new iteresting and fun content/additions.

- Custom Textures: Entire map is made from custom textures that I created myself, there is no default textures from the editor at all.

- Sounds: Some nice/funny startup sounds and some special gameplay sounds in the map. (from mario kart: 64)

- Level Improvements: Fixed all sorts of bugs/leaks from the old map.

- Level Addition: New funny skybox with a spinning sun at the bottom of the map, a jail that players will get teleported into instead of just dying when they fall out of the map and a bridge with some platforms under the map that hosts a small addition/secret.

Also, credits to the guy who created the first map, who apparently nobody knows of..
